HEADER: Kawahara & Zamma (2014) - Generative treatments of rendaku
TITLE: Generative treatments of rendaku
AUTHORTITLE: Kawahara & Zamma (2014)
RAWAUTHORS: <a href="/lingbuzz/002172?_s=xnSux4qTNg62zrki&amp;_k=iUk9aMew44GlYaxp&amp;1">Shigeto Kawahara</a>, <a href="/lingbuzz/002172?_s=xnSux4qTNg62zrki&amp;_k=iUk9aMew44GlYaxp&amp;2">Hideki Zamma</a>
AUTHORS: Shigeto Kawahara, Hideki Zamma
LASTNAMES: Kawahara, Zamma
MONTH: December
YEAR: 2014
ABSTRACT: This chapter provides an overview of how rendaku has been analyzed in the history of generative phonology, the mainstream framework of theoretical phonology.
